Nigerian Singer and rapper, Burna Boy shared a short video on his Instagram Stories of himself and British Singer and rapper, Stefflon Don cuddled up in bed, suggesting wild romance. Moments later, the beautiful Stefflon Don reacted on her Instagram story with a post confirming a relationship with Burna, but that they were yet to do whatever the initial video shared by Burna Boy suggested. But the fans ain’t having it… So many of his fans, especially the females are predictably reacting in the line of jealousy and heartbreak.